(42, 'App Information', 'app-information', 'a:1:{s:7:\"content\";s:2113:\"<div class=\"raw-info\"><img class=\"logo\" src=\"http://risk90.com.au/data/image/Logo.png\" style=\"height:137px; width:583px\" />\n<div>VERSION 1.0</div>\n</div>\n\n<p>So you have purchased the Raw90&deg;app! Well done. You now have in the palm of your hand the go-to opportunity assessment app used by entrepreneurs, innovators, SME&rsquo;s and start-ups all over the world.</p>\n\n<p>Raw90&deg; will allow you as an individual or as a team to assess the strengths and weaknesses of your next venture. Based on over 40 years of quantitative research, from some of the world&rsquo;s leading experts in the fields of entrepreneurship, commercialisation and innovation, Raw90&deg; will ask the hard questions every successful venture needs to be able to answer.</p>\n\n<p>Raw90&deg; is currently being utilised by The University of Adelaide&rsquo;s Entrepreneurship MOOC (Massive Online Open Course), hosted on the Harvard and MIT edX Platform</p>\n\n<p>The Raw90&deg; advantage:</p>\n\n<p>● Over 100 questions from key categories including Opportunity, Team, Resources and Environment</p>\n\n<p>● Responses plotted against a target base score on easy to read radar graphs</p>\n\n<p>● Graphs clearly define the strengths and weaknesses of the venture against the base correct practice methodology</p>\n\n<p>● Insightful and directional feedback given to all responses</p>\n\n<p>● Easy to share your project, graphs and outcome information with team members</p>\n\n<p>● Up to 5 team member&rsquo;s input data can be overlaid in radar graphs for comparison of strengths and weaknesses of venture</p>\n\n<p>Raw90&deg; is part of a suite of apps developed under the 90&deg;Ready brand, which have been created to help entrepreneur&rsquo;s, startup&rsquo;s and SME&rsquo;s, to have a clearer understanding of a venture&rsquo;s strengths and weaknesses. Our aim is to ensure your next project is 90&deg;Ready, that&rsquo;s a 90&deg; trajectory heading in the right direction for financial success.</p>\n\n<p>Have a question, problem, or feedback? Reach out to us at <a href=\"mailto:feedback@ninetyready.com\">feedback@ninetyready.com</a></p>\n\";}', '2017-07-28 09:00:56', '2017-08-06 15:44:38', 'risk_content', 1, -1, -1, NULL, NULL, 41, '10018');
